                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-741-18620707 t18620707-741-punishment-25"></join>Confined Six Months</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Robert Malcolm Kerr, Esq.</hi>
